info.name: Windows 10 Style for Firefox
info.description: A simple yet beautiful theme, bringing the Windows 10 style to Firefox.
info.additionalInfo: I've not made this theme by scratch, I've used 10Fox as the base and some parts of Windows 10 Firefox Theme but revamped the color scheme, made some minor layout changes and fixed some bugs. I know there are still some bugs which I didn't fix yet and, also, it lacks a lot of themed icons to have that 'complete'. I don't promise to update this often, but if anything breaks I'll try to. Changelog - Identity-box color is now grey so it matches the rest of the theme. (25/08/2015) Credits HughesMDflyer4 - 10Fox creator maxxdogg - Windows 10 Firefox Theme creator
